metadata.name: soft, sweet smiles
metadata.description:
at a glance, her eyes contain the cosmos,  
exploding with delight  
equally sharing the fright  
of a self-destruction that can occur  
on site

at a glance, those ebonic flames  
mesmerize the suitor  
of a man who was never equipped for the coal  
men should know  
women are always cold.

at a glance. she is taking away the spirit bequeathed to a kite!  
Look into my eyes and tell me son, what is quite right  
about a soft, sweet smile, 
that promises the afternoon delight.  
//

September 2022
